high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the end of the kitchen island, then turn towards the island on your right.
Pick up the fork on the front left corner of the kitchen island.
Turn around and go to the sink behind you.
Place the fork to the left of the green sponge, in the sink.
Turn around and walk between the wall and the kitchen island, then turn to your right to face the island.
Pick up the fork, in front of the fry pan, on the kitchen island.
Turn to your left and go past the island then turn to your right and go to the kitchen sink on your left.
Place the fork in the sink, to the left of the other fork.
anns.task_desc: Put two forks in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the fork that's closest to you.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the fork inside of the sink.
Walk over to the kitchen island, facing the side of it.
Pick up the fork to the left of the sharp knife.
Walk back over to the sink.
Put the fork inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two forks to the sink.

high_descs: turn left then walk straight towards the stove then turn right towards the table
pick up the fork near the edge of the table
turn right and walk straight then turn right again and walk straight towards the sink
put the fork down into the sink
turn left then walk straight then turn left again and then turn right at the wall then left again then walk straight and turn left at the edge of the green table
pick up the fork off of the edge of the table
turn left then walk to the end of the table then turn right and walk straight then turn left again and walk towards the sink
put the fork into the sink next to the other fork
anns.task_desc: clean up forks and put them into the sink
